                   <p>
                      <lb n="1"/>śrīcandrādityācāryyākhyajīnasūto <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>śak<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> kuśalaḥ <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/>
                      <lb n="2"/>śīlācūram upetī jñānasakalāṁ nānābhidharmmasya jñānavid vahubhaveṣu
                      <lb n="3"/>Ātmāparasagaṇena satvasakalāṁ māraś <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> sainyaś ca kleśavdhīḥ <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/>
                      <lb n="4"/>sau ham pi kr̥tvāna bībīdhapprakārai <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/>āsaṇaiḥ
                   </p>
